{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/\u0411\u0435\u0437_\u043d\u0430\u0437\u0432\u0438__600_x_125_\u043f\u0456\u043a\u0441._.gif?t=1738959152\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome to the South Pole, where you will have to lift penguins!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Penguin Helper </strong>is a fun 3D first-person game in which you become a real hero to these funny creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/ezgif-5-ad29baca73.gif?t=1738959152\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take a walk among the snowy open spaces and watch the southern lights. But be careful! Penguins lose coordination as soon as a plane flies over them. Your task is to put them on their feet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/ezgif-5-deab326cd4.gif?t=1738959152\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore frosty landscapes, enjoy the beauty of vast expanses and skies, and enjoy the calm and tranquility of the South Pole.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/ezgif-5-f8b4a176fc.gif?t=1738959152\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The breathtaking expanses of the South Pole</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Interaction with penguins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Raising penguins as the main mechanic of the game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Meditative atmosphere with pleasant sound</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Counter of raised penguins</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2964280/extras/\u0414\u0438\u0437\u0430\u0438\u0306\u043d_\u0431\u0435\u0437_\u043d\u0430\u0437\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u044f__2_.png?t=1738959152\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready to become a real hero of the South Pole? Put on warm clothes, stock up on tea and start your Penguin Helper adventure![/IMG][]</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Penguin Apprentice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2964280/76793d15672c6f1fcead32c99f320cfa266ac537.jpg"},{"name":"Ice Catcher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2964280/24b596b8bd51334b78a106431a33c4bdde6ab419.jpg"},{"name":"Frost Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2964280/d757a728f8485a667ab53767f5dcebb7fd2f8be4.jpg"},{"name":"Polar Veteran","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2964280/9209edf915e85d4839b80fe53c1562c6d71baa78.jpg"},{"name":"Ice Guru","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2964280/e2b9ea1163aecb89f1e8ad21b3e579f65bf167c7.jpg"},{"name":"Arctic Adventurer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2964280/51e06c67b4392b58d6ea30d88c360a13c308aad6.jpg"},{"name":"Polar Sovereign","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2964280/86f14562eda89fb073cd3c5ee7a3d58d8b7b008d.jpg"},{"name":"Ice Guardian","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2964280/ce916e089f9d0730d4dfd47880f27b3e9fa170e3.jpg"},{"name":"Arctic Watcher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2964280/8bf1915631094c6aee99d1f6b5e9e93ae9bdf6e